# WordPress Theme Development with TailPress

## Theme Structure
- **Entry Point**: [themes/aratavietnam/functions.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/functions.php) - Main theme configuration
- **Template Files**: Standard WordPress template hierarchy
- **Assets**: [themes/aratavietnam/resources/](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/resources/) - Source files
- **Build Output**: [themes/aratavietnam/dist/](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/dist/) - Compiled assets

## TailPress Framework
- **Theme Instance**: Use `aratavietnam()` function for configuration
- **Asset Management**: Vite integration with Tailwind CSS
- **Component System**: Modular structure in [themes/aratavietnam/inc/](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/inc/)
- **Template Parts**: Reusable components in [themes/aratavietnam/template-parts/](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/template-parts/)

## Key Components
- **WooCommerce**: [themes/aratavietnam/inc/woocommerce.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/inc/woocommerce.php)
- **Contact Form**: [themes/aratavietnam/inc/contact-form.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/inc/contact-form.php)
- **News System**: [themes/aratavietnam/inc/news-post-types.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/inc/news-post-types.php)
- **Vietnamese Fonts**: [themes/aratavietnam/inc/fonts-vietnamese.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/inc/fonts-vietnamese.php)

## CSS Architecture
- **Main Styles**: [themes/aratavietnam/resources/css/app.css](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/resources/css/app.css)
- **Custom Styles**: [themes/aratavietnam/resources/css/custom.css](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/resources/css/custom.css)
- **Theme Variables**: [themes/aratavietnam/resources/css/theme.css](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/resources/css/theme.css)
- **Tailwind Config**: Automatic integration with brand colors

## Development Workflow
1. Edit files in `resources/` directory
2. Use `npm run dev` for hot reload
3. Use `npm run build` for production
4. Assets automatically compiled to `dist/`

## WordPress Integration
- **Custom Post Types**: Contact submissions, News articles
- **Meta Fields**: Editable content for pages
- **Admin Interface**: Custom admin panels
- **Security**: Nonce verification, input sanitization
